<plot>Desperate for a date, a young man scours a local coffee shop for the perfect woman. Judging them by how they take their coffee, he envisions what each woman might be like in a relationship, and leaves the shop dateless. Not a moment later, the tables are turned. He learns the hard way about keeping an open mind.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?562823</url></doc>
